  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, Lu et al. [41] investigate strategic adversarial attacks in AI-assisted decision-making to reduce human trust and reliance.",
    "In this context, Xiong et al. [42] could offer valuable insights into sentiment analysis, albeit in a different domain.One key advantage lies in the ability of LLMs to understand and process the intricate language used in legal texts.",
    "Legal documents often contain nuanced structures, complex terminology, and context-dependent meanings.",
    "Large Language Models, with their extensive pre-training on diverse datasets, showcase a remarkable capacity to capture the subtleties of legal language.",
    "This inherent linguistic understanding positions LLMs as powerful tools for extracting meaningful information from legal citations."
  ]
}